'''露比·蘿絲·朗根海姆'''（{{lang-en|Ruby Rose Langenheim}}，{{bd|1986年|3月20日}}）或簡稱'''露比·蘿絲'''（{{lang-en|Ruby Rose}}），是一位[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[女演員|女演員]]、[[模特兒|模特兒]]和[[電視節目主持人|電視節目主持人]]。較著名的是在電視節目《[[澳洲超級模特兒新秀大賽|澳洲超級模特兒新秀大賽]]》（2009年）與《{{link-en|The Project (澳洲電視節目)|The Project (Australian TV program)|The Project}}》（2009年至2011年）中擔任主持人之一。2016年，她出演《[[惡靈古堡：最終章|惡靈古堡：最終章]]》而知名度大增。

2015年開始參演[[Netflix|Netflix]]電視劇《[[勁爆女子監獄|勁爆女子監獄]]》，並因此獲得好評<ref name="Inquisitr">{{cite web |url=http://www.inquisitr.com/2188259/ruby-rose-has-something-to-say-to-women-going-gay-for-her/ |title=Ruby Rose has something to say to women 'going gay' for her |publisher=Inquisitr.com |date=2015-06-20 |accessdate=2015-07-16}}</ref>。她還主演了2019年的CW電視劇《蝙蝠女俠》。

==早年生活==
蘿絲出生於[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]的一個單親家庭，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wearitwithpride.com.au/law-reforms/relationships/ruby-rose/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100207093940/http://www.wearitwithpride.com.au/law-reforms/relationships/ruby-rose/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=7 February 2010 |title=Ruby Rose – Relationships – Wear It With Pride |publisher=wearitwithpride.com.au |access-date=28 March 2015}}</ref> 母親名字叫Katia Langenheim，是一位藝術家，蘿絲稱其為她的榜樣之一。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0,21985,25528021-5006024,00.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527011252/http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0,21985,25528021-5006024,00.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=27 May 2009 |title=MTV star Ruby Rose's dark past |access-date=30 May 2009 |date=24 May 2009 |work=Herald Sun |first1=Kim |last1=Wilson}}</ref>蘿絲自小經常頻繁往來多州，她曾在[[維多利亞州|維多利亞州]]、[[塔斯馬尼亞州|塔斯馬尼亞州]]和[[布里斯本|布里斯本]]等地居住過，最後定居墨爾本。

==個人生活==
露比·蘿絲在12歲時就已經是名[[出櫃|出櫃]]的女同性戀<ref name="Fired up">{{cite web |title=Ruby Rose is back on TV and she's 'fired up and excited about everything again' |date=2015-05-17 |accessdate=2015-07-13 |publisher=[[News.com.au|News.com.au]] |url=http://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/sunday-style/ruby-rose-is-back-on-tv-and-shes-fired-up-and-excited-about-everything-again/story-fnrmugv2-1227357715339 |archive-date=2015-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814224756/http://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/sunday-style/ruby-rose-is-back-on-tv-and-shes-fired-up-and-excited-about-everything-again/story-fnrmugv2-1227357715339 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ruby">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/yoursay/index.php/dailytelegraph/comments/ruby_rose_live_blog/P0/ |title=Ruby Rose – live blog |accessdate=2008-11-25 |date=2008-03-28 |publisher=news.com.au |archive-date=2016-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125061101/http://blogs.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/yoursay/index.php/dailytelegraph/comments/ruby_rose_live_blog/P0/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。基於蘿絲的性向，使她常受到同學言語辱罵和身體虐待等[[霸凌|霸凌]]，而導致她曾有自殺傾向<ref name="Fired up"/>。她還為此受到了[[兒童性虐待|兒童性虐待]]<ref name="Demons">{{cite web |title=Ruby Rose confronts her demons |date=2013-05-22 |accessdate=2015-07-13 |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/celebrity/ruby-rose-confronts-her-demons/story-fni0bn79-1226647926640}}</ref>，以及患有[[躁鬱症|躁鬱症]]和[[重性憂鬱障礙|重性憂鬱障礙]]<ref name="Fired up"/>。

蘿絲曾透露，長大後的她想藉由賺錢來使自己從[[變性|女性變成男性]]<ref name="Borden">{{cite web |last=Borden |first=J.D. |title=10 Things You Want To Know About Ruby Rose, 'Orange is the New Black's New Heartbreaker |date=2015-06-23 |accessdate=2015-07-13 |work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]] |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/bent/10-things-you-want-to-know-about-ruby-rose-orange-is-the-new-blacks-new-heartbreaker-20150623 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722015739/http://blogs.indiewire.com/bent/10-things-you-want-to-know-about-ruby-rose-orange-is-the-new-blacks-new-heartbreaker-20150623 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。但後來，她還是決定維持著女性的身份，並對自己現在的樣子感到舒適<ref name="Jarvis">{{cite web |last=Jarvis |first=Erika |title=Ruby Rose: 'I used to pray to God that I wouldn’t get breasts' |date=2014-07-25 |accessdate=2015-07-13 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jul/25/ruby-rose-video-break-free-gender}}</ref>。

蘿絲是一位嚴格素食者，她曾在推特發表過素食與保護動物的相關言論，包括反對鬥牛、提醒大家吃素改變氣候變遷。<ref name="Ruby Rose Hopes Fans Make the Change for Climate Change">{{cite web |title=Ruby Rose Hopes Fans Make the Change for Climate Change|date=2017-04-06 |publisher=[[善待動物組織|善待動物組織]] |url=https://www.peta.org/blog/ruby-rose-urges-followers-stop-eating-animals/}}</ref>

2016年11月7日，證實蘿絲與[[雙面維若妮卡|雙面維若妮卡]]的女歌手{{le|潔西卡·歐莉葛里雅索|Jessica Origliasso}}正在交往中。兩人曾於2008年交往過，後來分手，但於2016年10月31日，兩人在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上發照片代表她們又再度復合<ref name="Gray">{{cite web |last=Gray |first=Mark |title=RUBY ROSE AND EX JESS ORIGLIASSO REUNITE EIGHT YEARS AFTER SPLIT |date=2016-11-07 |accessdate=2016-11-08 |work=Wonderwall.com |url=http://www.wonderwall.com/news/ruby-rose-the-veronicas-jess-origliasso-back-together-dating-again-1945043.article}}</ref>。2018年4月，告知她們早在幾個月前就分手了，但依然非常支持她，可知是和平分手。

2019年9月，蘿絲自行表示，她在拍片時因一特技演出的失誤而造成兩側[[椎间盘脱出症|椎間盤突出]]，為此接受了緊急背部手術<ref>{{cite web |title=Ruby Rose reveals she 'risked becoming paralysed,' underwent emergency surgery after stunt injuries|date=2019-09-28 |publisher=[[Nine.com.au|Nine.com.au]] |url=https://celebrity.nine.com.au/latest/ruby-rose-shares-graphic-video-of-emergency-surgery-stunt-injuries/25705466-3853-42bf-8775-e2833675d799}}</ref>。

